I"—®<h3 id="22-е°ҪйҮҸз”Ёиҫ…еҠ©зұ»жқҘз»ҙжҠӨзЁӢеәҸзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒиҖҢдёҚиҰҒз”Ёеӯ—е…ёе’Ңе…ғз»„">22. е°ҪйҮҸз”Ёиҫ…еҠ©зұ»жқҘз»ҙжҠӨзЁӢеәҸзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒпјҢиҖҢдёҚиҰҒз”Ёеӯ—е…ёе’Ңе…ғз»„</h3>

<ul>
  <li>дёҚиҰҒдҪҝз”ЁеҢ…еҗ«е…¶е®ғеӯ—е…ёзҡ„еӯ—е…ёпјҢд№ҹдёҚиҰҒдҪҝз”ЁиҝҮй•ҝзҡ„е…ғз»„</li>
  <li>еҰӮжһңе®№еҷЁдёӯеҢ…еҗ«з®ҖеҚ•еҸҲдёҚеҸҜеҸҳзҡ„ж•°жҚ®пјҢйӮЈд№ҲеҸҜд»Ҙе…ҲдҪҝз”Ё namedtupleжқҘиЎЁзӨәпјҢеҫ…зЁҚеҗҺжңүйңҖиҰҒж—¶пјҢеҶҚдҝ®ж”№дёәе®Ңж•ҙзҡ„зұ»</li>
  <li>дҝқеӯҳеҶ…йғЁзҠ¶жҖҒзҡ„еӯ—е…ёеҰӮжһңеҸҳеҫ—жҜ”иҫғеӨҚжқӮпјҢйӮЈе°ұеә”иҜҘжҠҠиҝҷдәӣд»Јз ҒжӢҶи§ЈеӨ–еӨҡдёӘиҫ…еҠ©зұ»</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># иҰҒжҠҠи®ёеӨҡеӯҰз”ҹзҡ„жҲҗз»©и®°еҪ•дёӢжқҘпјҢдҪҶиҝҷдәӣеӯҰз”ҹзҡ„еҗҚеӯ—жҲ‘д»¬дәӢе…ҲдёҚзҹҘйҒ“гҖӮдәҺжҳҜе®ҡд№үдәҶдёҖдёӘзұ»пјҢжҠҠеӯҰз”ҹеҗҚеӯ—е…ЁйғЁдҝқеӯҳеңЁеӯ—е…ёйҮҢйқўпјҢиҝҷж ·е°ұдёҚз”ЁжҠҠжҜҸдёӘеӯҰз”ҹиЎЁзӨәжҲҗеҜ№иұЎдәҶпјҢд№ҹж— йңҖеңЁжҜҸдёӘеҜ№иұЎдёӯйў„и®ҫдёҖдёӘеӯҳеңЁе…¶еҗҚеӯ—зҡ„еұһжҖ§
</span>
<span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">SimpleGradebook</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">object</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">__init__</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">_grades</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">add_student</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">_grades</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
    
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">report_grade</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">score</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">_grades</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">].</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">score</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">average_grade</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="n">grades</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">_grades</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">]</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">grades</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">grades</span><span class="p">)</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="23-з®ҖеҚ•зҡ„жҺҘеҸЈеә”иҜҘжҺҘеҸ—еҮҪж•°иҖҢдёҚжҳҜзұ»зҡ„е®һдҫӢ">23. з®ҖеҚ•зҡ„жҺҘеҸЈеә”иҜҘжҺҘеҸ—еҮҪж•°пјҢиҖҢдёҚжҳҜзұ»зҡ„е®һдҫӢ</h3>

<ul>
  <li>еҜ№дәҺиҝһжҺҘеҗ„з§Қpythonз»„д»¶зҡ„з®ҖеҚ•жҺҘеҸЈжқҘиҜҙпјҢйҖҡеёёеә”иҜҘз»ҷе…¶зӣҙжҺҘдј е…ҘеҮҪж•°пјҢиҖҢдёҚжҳҜе…Ҳе®ҡд№үжҹҗдёӘзұ»пјҢз„¶еҗҺеҶҚдј е…ҘиҜҘзұ»зҡ„е®һдҫӢ</li>
  <li>pythonдёӯзҡ„еҮҪж•°е’Ңж–№жі•йғҪеҸҜд»ҘеғҸдёҖзә§зұ»йӮЈж ·еј•з”ЁпјҢеӣ жӯӨпјҢд»–д»¬дёҺе…¶е®ғзұ»еһӢзҡ„еҜ№иұЎдёҖж ·пјҢд№ҹиғҪеӨҹж”ҫеңЁиЎЁиҫҫејҸйҮҢйқў</li>
  <li>йҖҡиҝҮеҗҚдёә <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">__call__</code> зҡ„зү№ж®Ҡж–№жі•пјҢеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝзұ»зҡ„зӨәдҫӢиғҪеӨҹеғҸжҷ®йҖҡзҡ„pythonеҮҪж•°йӮЈж ·еҫ—еҲ°и°ғз”Ё</li>
  <li>еҰӮжһңиҰҒз”ЁеҮҪж•°дҝқеӯҳзҠ¶жҖҒпјҢйӮЈе°ұеә”иҜҘе®ҡд№үж–°зҡ„зұ»пјҢе№¶д»Өе…¶е®һзҺ° <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">__call__</code>ж–№жі•пјҢиҖҢдёҚиҰҒе®ҡд№үеёҰзҠ¶жҖҒзҡ„й—ӯеҢ…</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># Example 1
</span><span class="n">names</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'Socrates'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'Archimedes'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'Plato'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'Aristotle'</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">names</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sort</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">lambda</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">names</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 2
</span><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">collections</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">defaultdict</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">log_missing</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Key added'</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">0</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 3
</span><span class="n">current</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s">'green'</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'blue'</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">}</span>
<span class="n">increments</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span>
    <span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'red'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">),</span>
    <span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'blue'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">17</span><span class="p">),</span>
    <span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'orange'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">),</span>
<span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">result</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">defaultdict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">log_missing</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">current</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Before:'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">dict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">result</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">amount</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">increments</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">result</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">amount</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'After: '</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">dict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">result</span><span class="p">))</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 4
# зҺ°еңЁиҰҒз»ҷdefaultdictдј е…ҘдёҖдёӘдә§з”ҹй»ҳи®ӨеҖјзҡ„жҢӮй’©пјҢе№¶д»Өе…¶з»ҹи®ЎеҮәиҜҘеӯ—е…ёдёҖе…ұйҒҮеҲ°дәҶеӨҡе°‘
# зјәеӨұзҡ„й”®гҖӮдёҖз§Қе®һзҺ°ж–№ејҸжҳҜдҪҝз”ЁеёҰзҠ¶жҖҒзҡ„й—ӯеҢ…гҖӮдёӢйқўе®ҡд№үзҡ„иҫ…еҠ©еҮҪж•°е°ұжҳҜдҪҝз”Ёиҝҷз§Қй—ӯеҢ…
# дҪңдёәдә§з”ҹй»ҳи®ӨеҖјзҡ„жҢӮй’©еҮҪж•°
</span><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">increment_with_report</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">current</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">increments</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">added_count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">missing</span><span class="p">():</span>
        <span class="k">nonlocal</span> <span class="n">added_count</span>  <span class="c1"># Stateful closure
</span>        <span class="n">added_count</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">0</span>

    <span class="n">result</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">defaultdict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">missing</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">current</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">amount</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">increments</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">result</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">amount</span>

    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">result</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">added_count</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 5
</span><span class="n">result</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">increment_with_report</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">current</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">increments</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">assert</span> <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">result</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 6
# жҠҠеёҰзҠ¶жҖҒзҡ„й—ӯеҢ…еҮҪж•°з”ЁдҪңжҢӮй’©жңүдёҖдёӘзјәзӮ№пјҢе°ұжҳҜиҜ»иө·жқҘиҰҒжҜ”ж— зҠ¶жҖҒзҡ„еҮҪж•°йҡҫжҮӮдёҖдәӣгҖӮиҝҳжңүдёӘ
# еҠһжі•пјҢе®ҡд№үдёҖдёӘе°ҸеһӢзҡ„зұ»пјҢжҠҠйңҖиҰҒиҝҪиёӘзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒе°ҒиЈ…иө·жқҘ
</span><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">CountMissing</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">object</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">__init__</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">added</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">missing</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">added</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">0</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 7
</span><span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">CountMissing</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">result</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">defaultdict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">missing</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">current</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># Method reference
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">amount</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">increments</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">result</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">amount</span>
<span class="k">assert</span> <span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">added</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">result</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 8
# дҪҝз”ЁдҫӢ7зЎ®е®һжҜ”й—ӯеҢ…еҮҪж•°еҘҪзӮ№пјҢдҪҶжҳҜжҲ‘д»¬дҫқз„¶дёҚеӨӘе®№жҳ“зҗҶи§ЈCountMissing зҡ„ж„ҸеӣҫгҖӮCountMissing
# еҜ№иұЎз”ұи°ҒжқҘжһ„е»әпјҹmissingж–№жі•з”ұи°ҒжқҘи°ғз”ЁпјҹиҜҘзұ»д»ҘеҗҺжҳҜеҗҰйңҖиҰҒж·»еҠ ж–°зҡ„е…¬е…ұж–№жі•пјҹиҝҷдәӣй—®йўҳпјҢйғҪ
# еҝ…йЎ»зӯүзңӢиҝҮдәҶdefaultdictзҡ„з”Ёжі•д№ӢеҗҺпјҢжүҚиғҪжҳҺзҷҪгҖӮ 
# дёәдәҶи§ЈеҶіиҝҷдәӣй—®йўҳпјҢжҲ‘д»¬еҸҜд»ҘеңЁд»Јз Ғдёӯе®ҡд№үеҗҚдёә __call__ зҡ„зү№ж®Ҡж–№жі•гҖӮиҜҘж–№жі•дҪҝзӣёе…іеҜ№иұЎиғҪеӨҹ
# еғҸеҮҪж•°йӮЈж ·еҫ—еҲ°и°ғз”ЁгҖӮжӯӨеӨ–еҰӮжһңжҠҠиҝҷж ·зҡ„е®һдҫӢдј з»ҷеҶ…зҪ®зҡ„callableеҮҪж•°пјҢйӮЈд№ҲcallableеҮҪж•°дјҡиҝ”еӣһTrue
</span><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">BetterCountMissing</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">object</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">__init__</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">added</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">__call__</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">added</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">0</span>

<span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">BetterCountMissing</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="k">assert</span> <span class="nb">callable</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="c1"># Example 9
</span><span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">BetterCountMissing</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">result</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">defaultdict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">current</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># Relies on __call__
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">amount</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">increments</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">result</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">amount</span>
<span class="k">assert</span> <span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">added</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">result</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="24-д»Ҙ-classmethod-еҪўејҸзҡ„еӨҡжҖҒеҺ»йҖҡз”Ёең°жһ„е»әеҜ№иұЎ">24. д»Ҙ @classmethod еҪўејҸзҡ„еӨҡжҖҒеҺ»йҖҡз”Ёең°жһ„е»әеҜ№иұЎ</h3>

<p>еӨҡжҖҒпјҡдҪҝеҫ—з»§жүҝдҪ“зі»дёӯзҡ„еӨҡдёӘзұ»йғҪиғҪд»Ҙеҗ„иҮӘжүҖзӢ¬жңүзҡ„ж–№ејҸжқҘе®һзҺ°жҹҗдёӘж–№жі•гҖӮиҝҷдәӣзұ»пјҢйғҪж»Ўи¶ізӣёеҗҢзҡ„жҺҘеҸЈжҲ–з»§жүҝиҮӘзӣёеҗҢзҡ„жҠҪиұЎзұ»пјҢдҪҶеҚҙжңүзқҖеҗ„иҮӘдёҚеҗҢзҡ„еҠҹиғҪгҖӮ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># е®һзҺ°MapReduce зҡ„жөҒзЁӢ
</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">os</span>
